import React from 'react' export default function Rating(props) { const { rating, numReviews } = props; return (
< i className={rating >= 1 ? "fa fa-star" : rating >= 0.5 ? 'fa fa-star-half-o' : 'fa fa-star-o' } > < i className={rating >= 2 ? "fa fa-star" : rating >= 1.5 ? 'fa fa-star-half-o' : 'fa fa-star-o' } > < i className={rating >= 3 ? "fa fa-star" : rating >= 2.5 ? 'fa fa-star-half-o' : 'fa fa-star-o' } > < i className={rating >= 4 ? "fa fa-star" : rating >= 3.5 ? 'fa fa-star-half-o' : 'fa fa-star-o' } > < i className={rating >= 5 ? "fa fa-star" : rating >= 4.5 ? 'fa fa-star-half-o' : 'fa fa-star-o' } > {numReviews + 'reviews'}
) }
